The '''''Quamar Messenger''''' was a [[Passenger liner/Legends|passenger liner]] possibly operated by [[Haj Shipping Lines]]. It was older than the ''[[Queen of Empire]]'', and was hijacked by [[Gallandro/Legends|Gallandro]] on its maiden voyage.

